'''House Taneel''' was one of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] [[Ancient Houses]] and the ruling house of the planet [[Neelanon/Legends|Neelanon]] in the [[Senex sector/Legends|Senex sector]].

A member of this house, [[Terr Taneel/Legends|Terr Taneel]], was Neelanon's [[Senator/Legends|senator]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. [[Són Halliikeenovich]] of [[House Halliikeenovich]], an unimportant noble house in [[Juvex sector/Legends|Juvex sector]], hoped to gain his house prestige by marrying Taneel and joining their houses. If she returned his interest, it was not obvious to the public.

